    public abstract class ProtoBelongsToModule
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.function.Predicate<SourceFile>
    A predicate determining if a Protobuf file belongs to the specified module.

    The descendants of this class are supposed to work with different types of files, e.g. an original .proto file, a compiled .java, etc.
